</div>
<div id="ftn6">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref6" name="_ftn6"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[6]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> Cf. Chapitre 3 : « Son attitude d’offrande ».</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn7">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref7" name="_ftn7"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[7]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> <i>Compendium du catéchisme de l’Eglise catholique,</i> 2005, §105</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn8">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref8" name="_ftn8"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[8]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> <i>La Tradition Apostolique</i> § 21, par B.BOTTE, Sources chrétiennes 11 bis, Le Cerf, Paris 1968, p. 84</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn9">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref9" name="_ftn9"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[9]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT"> Cf. Ignazio <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Calabuig</span>, <i>Il culto di Maria in occidente</i>, In <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Pontificio Istituto Liturgico sant’Anselmo</span>, <i>Scientia Liturgica</i>, sotto la direzione di A.J. <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Chupungco</span>, vol V, Piemme 1998. p. 270-271</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn10">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref10" name="_ftn10"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[10]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> Cf. F. <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Breynaert</span>, <i>L’arbre de vie, symbole central de la théologie de Saint Louis-Marie de Montfort,</i> Editions Parole et silence, Paris 2006, p. 306, cf. aussi p. 279-295.</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn11">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref11" name="_ftn11"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[11]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> <span lang="FR-BE" style="text-transform: uppercase;">Paul VI,</span><span lang="FR-BE"> Exhortation pastorale <i>Marialis cultus</i> n° 35</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn12">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref12" name="_ftn12"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[12]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> En ce sens, on peut dire que Marie est une antidote à une éthique trop autonome ou à une idolâtrie de la raison humaine. Avec Marie, la raison éthique s’appuie sur la Rédemption.</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn13">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref13" name="_ftn13"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[13]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT"> Cf. A.<span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Serra</span>, <i>La profezia di Simeone (Lc 2,34-35) nella tradizione greco-latina dei secoli II-XIV Contenuti e proposte,</i> in Marianum 60 (1998) cf pp. 309-311 ; 377-381 ; A.<span style="text-transform: uppercase;"> Serra</span>, <i>La Spada : simbolo della Parola di Dio, nell’Antico Testamento biblico-giudaico e nel Nuovo Testamento,</i> in Marianum 63 (2001), pp. 17-89 ; A.<span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Valentini</span>, <i>Il secondo annuncio a Maria,</i> in Marianum 50 (1988), pp.290-322 ; G. <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Rosse</span>, <i>Approcci esegetici al testo della presentazione,</i> in Theotokos 6 (1998), pp 17-30</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn14">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref14" name="_ftn14"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[14]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT"> U. N<span style="text-transform: uppercase;">eri,</span> <i>Il cantico dei cantici. Antica interpretazione ebraica.</i> Città Nuova Editrice, Roma 1976, p. 120.</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn15">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref15" name="_ftn15"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[15]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="FR-BE"> Cf. Par exemple, Exode Rabba 2,4 sur Exode 3,1</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn16">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref16" name="_ftn16"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[16]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> Pour saint Ambroise, l’épée symbolise toute la parole de Jésus, tout le dessein de Dieu, et le Fiat de Marie dure toute sa vie. De même, Rupert de Deutz et Adam Scot s’appuient sur He 4,12. Origène s’appuie sur He 4,12 et le rapproche du scandale de la Passion.</p>
</div>
