</div>
<div id="ftn83">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref83" name="_ftn83"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[83]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> L. <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Le Crom,</span> <i>Un apôtre marial, saint Louis-Marie Grignion de Montfort,</i> édition les traditions françaises, Tourcoing 1946, p. 273</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn84">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref84" name="_ftn84"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[84]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> Cf. <span lang="FR-BE" style="text-transform: uppercase; mso-ansi-language: FR-BE;">Jean Paul</span> II, Audience générale du 20.08.03</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn85">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref85" name="_ftn85"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[85]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> D’où l’importance d’une pastorale de la paix pour que les chrétiens ne soient pas faibles et démunis lorsque se déchaînent des haines dans leur propre nation, dans leur propre ethnie, dans leur propre peuple.</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn86">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref86" name="_ftn86"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[86]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a> C’est ainsi que Pie XII en 1949 n’encouragea pas les diplomates français à lutter contre le régime communiste russe de manière ouverte et armée, mais à résister par des moyens non violents. Cf. Andréa <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Riccardi</span>,<i> La Pace preventiva, </i>San Paolo, Milan 2004, p. 150.</p>
</div>
<div id="ftn87">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/A%20Ecoute%20de%20Marie%202.%20Avec%20Marie%20dans%20la%20lumi%C3%A8re.docx#_ftnref87" name="_ftn87"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[87]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="FR-BE"> Au sens où l’entend <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Jean Paul II</span>, <i>Mémoire et identité</i>, Flammarion, Paris 2005, p. 82-85.</span></p>
